8\/salaam-coming-going\/","url_meta":{"origin":15431,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greet with peace when coming and going","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you arrives in a gathering, let him greet them with peace. When he intends to leave, let him leave them with peace. The first greeting is not more worthy than the last.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43066,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/13\/salaam-living-or-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":15431,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greeting with peace, living or dead","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Sulaym reported: I saw a man whose opinions the people took seriously. He would not say anything but that they accepted it. I said, \u201cWho is this?\u201d They said, \u201cThis is the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d I said twice, \u201cUpon you be peace,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11851,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/29\/dua-most-helpless-miser-bakhil\/","url_meta":{"origin":15431,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Most helpless are those who cannot pray","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most helpless of people are those unable to supplicate. The most miserly of people are those who are miserly with the greeting of peace.\u201d Grade: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 8767 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4437,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/end-salat-salaam-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15431,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet ends prayer with peace, mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Wa\u2019il ibn Hujr reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he would end by invoking peace on his right side, saying, \u201cPeace be upon you, the mercy of Allah, and His blessings,\u201d and again to his left side, saying, \u201cPeace and mercy of Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25657,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/20\/ali-din-deen-opinion-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":15431,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Deen: Religion is based on revelation, not opinion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 20, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abd Khayr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf the religion were based up